is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module lets you manage partner's subscriptions to your company's main mailing list\ndirectly from the partner form.\n\nIt makes it easier to manage partner communications, specially if you only use a single\nmailing list.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nGo to Email Marketing > Settings and configure your Company Newsletter mailing list.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues/new?body=module:%20mass_mailing_company_newsletter%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Camptocamp](https://www.camptocamp.com)\n\n  > - Iv\u00e1n Todorovich \\<<mailto:ivan.todorovich@gmail.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-ivantodorovich }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/social](https://github.com/OCA/social/tree/14.0/mass_mailing_company_newsletter) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_company", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models..res_company", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_config_settings", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models..res_config_settings", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_partner", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models..res_partner", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_config_settings", "documentation": ["Copyright 2021 Camptocamp (http://www.camptocamp.com).", "@author Iv\u00e1n Todorovich <ivan.todorovich@gmail.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_config_settings.ResConfigSettings", "bases": ["models.TransientModel"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_config_settings.ResConfigSettings._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_config_settings.ResConfigSettings.main_mailing_list_id", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mass_mailing_company_newsletter.models.res_company", "documentation": ["Copyright 2021 Camptocamp (http://www.camptocamp.com).", "@author Iv\u00e1n Todorovich <ivan.todorovich@gmail.com>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": 